        Parameters:
        bufferRegistration - The registration message to which this update is referring to
        timestamp - The moment when this constructor is called
        validFrom - This timestamp indicates from which moment on this update is valid.
        currentFillLevel - This value represents the current fill level of the buffer.
        currentRunningMode - This is a set of zero or more current running modes. For every actuator there will be one current running mode.
